&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="127828" author="green" created="Fri, 18 Sep 2015 18:03:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;did you try mounting with &quot;-o flock&quot; on the client?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="127821" author="dinatale2" created="Fri, 18 Sep 2015 17:47:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is a test system. We can obtain any information to help diagnose the issue. flock also succeeded on a Lustre 2.5.3 file system.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
